# Wix × First Bank FOCAS Payment Provider

This repository provides a reference implementation for integrating **Wix Velo Payment Provider Service Plugin** with **First Bank / FISC FOCAS credit card payment flow**.

This project demonstrates:

- Wix Payment Provider Service Plugin setup
- Hosted payment redirect flow
- HTML Form POST redirect to FOCAS
- Wix HTTP Functions callback handling
- Wix CMS payment record logging
- Success / failed payment return pages
- Optional Wix Orders payment status update through `submitEvent()`

> This repository is for educational and integration reference only.  
> Do not commit real merchant credentials, bank credentials, verification keys, callback secrets, or production transaction records.

---

## Architecture

```text
Wix Checkout
  ↓
FirstBank.js createTransaction()
  ↓
Save pending payment data to FocasPendingOrders
  ↓
Redirect to /_functions/focasRedirect?lidm=...
  ↓
http-functions.js generates HTML Form POST
  ↓
FOCAS hosted credit card payment page
  ↓
FOCAS posts payment result to /_functions/focasCallback
  ↓
Wix saves payment result to FocasOrders
  ↓
Optional submitEvent() updates Wix Orders
  ↓
Redirect to /payment-success or /payment-failed
